  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para><list>
<item>State the forces that act on a simple pendulum</item>
<item>Determine the angular frequency, frequency, and period of a simple pendulum in terms of the length of the pendulum and the acceleration due to gravity</item>
<item>Define the period for a physical pendulum</item>
<item>Define the period for a torsional pendulum</item>
</list></md:abstract>
